     8	class SlimManager:
     9	    """SlimManager responsible for slim operations such as finding available slim in given ontologies and showing slim
    10	    content.
    11	    """
    12	
    13	    @staticmethod
    14	    def get_slim_list(ontology: str) -> List[Dict[str, str]]:
    15	        """Returns name and definition of available slims in given ontology.
    16	
    17	        Args:
    18	            ontology: Ontology name
    19	
    20	        Returns:
    21	            Slim names and definitions list
    22	
    23	        """
    24	        slim_list: Dict[str, Slim] = dict()
    25	        result = run_sparql_query(get_slim_list_query(ontology))
    26	        for res in result:
    27	            slim_list.update(
    28	                {res.get("label"): Slim(name=res.get("label"), description=res.get("comment"))}
    29	            )
    30	        return [
    31	            {"name": slim.get_name(), "description": slim.get_description()}
    32	            for slim in slim_list.values()
    33	        ]
    34	
    35	    @staticmethod
    36	    def get_slim_members(slim_list: List[str]) -> List[str]:
    37	        """Lists names and IDs of all terms in slim.
    38	
    39	        Args:
    40	            slim_list: A list of slim names
    41	
    42	        Returns:
    43	            Term IRIs of the slim members
    44	
    45	        """
    46	        return [
    47	            term.get("term")
    48	            for slim_name in slim_list
    49	            for term in run_sparql_query(get_slim_members_query(slim_name))
    50	        ]
